news.title: Sequoia Capital India sells stake in Indigo Paints for Rs 210 crore
news.para: ​According to the bulk deal data available with the BSE, Sequoia Capital India Investments IV and SCI Investments V sold a total of 15,60,000 shares, amounting to 3.28 per cent stake in the company.

news.title: Royal family of Travancore to sell Delhi bungalow, plots for Rs 250 crore
news.para: According to news reports in 2019, the royal family had written to the central government, seeking return of the property, claiming that the Kerala government had only possession rights on it.

news.title: Sajjan India's promoter buys duplex in Mumbai's Worli for Rs 153 crore
news.para: Aggarwal has purchased the apartment with 15,337 sq ft built-up space in one of the towers of the super-premium residential project 360 West from Oasis Realty, a subsidiary of the project’s developer, Oberoi Developers, on Dr. Annie Besant Road.

news.title: Orient Cement posts loss of Rs 9 crore in Q2 FY23
news.para: Revenue from operation was marginally up at Rs 615.28 crore as against Rs 613.12 crore in the year-ago period. Total expenses in September quarter were Rs 630.19 crore, up 18.8 per cent from the year-ago period.

news.title: China's security agency in Hong Kong buys $65 million luxury villa
news.para: The 666-square metre (7,171-square foot) mansion has five bedrooms, three car parking spaces, a garden, its own lift and is described by its developer as "a residential jewel that secures panoramic views, low density and luxuriant living".

news.title: Chinese property stocks soar on fresh regulatory support
news.para: CIFI Holdings (Group) Co Ltd soared 40% while Country Garden Holdings Co Ltd surged 23%. The Hang Seng Mainland Properties Index rose 8%.

news.title: Bank of Maharashtra raises one-year MCLR by 10 bps
news.para: The benchmark one-year MCLR, used to price most of consumer loans such as auto, personal and home, has been revised upwards to 7.90 per cent from 7.80 per cent, the lender said in a regulatory filing.

news.title: Orient Bell's net profit dips 31% in Q2 FY23
news.para: The company's net consolidated income stood at Rs 174.65 crore in Q2 FY23, a growth of 3.75 per cent from Rs 168.33 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Nuvoco Vistas' net loss widens to Rs 130.38 crore in Q2 FY23
news.para: The company's net consolidated income stood at Rs 2,402.54 crore in Q2 FY23, a growth of 18.54 per cent from Rs 2,026.72 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Godrej Properties' net profit up 87.60% in Q2 FY23
news.para: The company's net consolidated income stood at Rs 369.20 crore in Q2 FY23, a growth of 10.47 per cent from Rs 334.22 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Enforcement directorate freezes Rs 50 crore of Salarpuria Sattva group
news.para: The ED found that the real estate company entered into a transaction with the scam-hit Heera Group and money has been routed to shel firms.

news.title: Uttarakhand: Only 14 of 195 brick kilns in Haridwar 'run with permits'
news.para: The air quality index (AQI) was at 165 on Tuesday. Environmentalists said that despite the Ganga flowing through the district, the poor air quality shows that various other factors are adding to the air pollution in the district.

news.title: Ramco Cements' net profit dips 99.28% in Q2 FY23
news.para: The company's net consolidated income stood at Rs 1,800.61 crore in Q2 FY23, a growth of 19.22 per cent from Rs 1,510.33 crore it recorded in the similar quarter last year.

news.title: Mumbai: Consumer forum directs probe against Khar housing society
news.para: The complainant housing society had moved the commission in 2012 seeking several reliefs, including demarcation with boundary walls between the two buildings, possession of the society office and parking spaces.

news.title: Residents of other Chintels Paradiso towers demand authorities to expedite audit
news.para: Now, residents of towers G and H have complained that there are several structural defects in these two towers, such as visible cracks in balconies and seepage.
